WILLIE C. MORGAN v. STATE OF FLORIDA 21 So. (2nd) 217

January Term, 1915

March 13, 1945 Division A B. L. Solomon, for appellant. J. Tom Watson, Attorney General, and John C. Wynn; -Assistant Attorney General, for appellee. PER CURIAM:'

■ On motion of the State the judgment is affirmed on authority of Lane, et al., v. State, 154 Fla. 853, 19 So. (2nd) 366.

CHAPMAN, C. J., TERRELL, BUFORD and ADAMS, JJ;, concur.
